title: AirTech-UK Bathroom Extractor Fan Nea Style White Front with Timer and Humidistat
features: Sleek White Front Panel: Geometric square design with softly rounded corners, made from durable white ABS plastic for a modern, discreet look that complements any interior.
Easy Installation: Front panels attach via special latches, making installation or removal quick and hassle-free.
Multiple Fan Options: Choose from four models – Standard, with Timer, with Humidity Sensor, or with Pull Cord – to suit your ventilation needs.
High-Quality Build: Made from durable ABS plastic with ball bearings, ensuring longevity and smooth operation.
Versatile Use: IPX4 protection rating and ability to handle temperatures up to 40°C; suitable for ceiling installation and use with non-return valves (ZZ).
Built-in Timer – Automatically turns off the fan with a customizable delay (ranging from 3 to 30 minutes) after the light has been switched off, ensuring optimal ventilation and energy efficiency.

Built-in Humidity Sensor – Constantly powered exhaust fans activate when moisture is detected in the room. They automatically switch off after a regulated delay of 3 to 30 minutes, providing efficient humidity control.
Specs: Voltage: 230V/50Hz, Consumption: 7W, Max Flow Rate: 105m3/h, Protection class: IP-X4, Max Noise Level: 28dB(A)
